      "post_id" : 31696584,
      "comment_id" : 51333311,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Because Optional means that it can be present, or absent. Absent != null. <code>null</code> in this case means &quot;I expect foobar to be present, but due to a bug it is null&quot;. <code>Optional.isPresent() == false</code> means foobar is not present, ie this is expected, legitimate behaviour."
