    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Optional should mainly be used for results of Services anyway. In the service you know what you have at hand and return Optional.of(someValue) if you have a result and return Optional.empty() if you don't. In this case, someValue should never be null and still, you return an Optional.</p>\n"
